.chiselled\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1\">chiselled\u003C/rs>\n                                \t\u003Cdamage ana=\"#text_condition.complete\"/>\n\t\t\t\u003C/layout>\n                            \u003C/layoutDesc>\n                        \u003C/objectDesc>\n                        \u003ChandDesc>\n                            \u003ChandNote>\u003Cp>cursive and majiscule alpha, uncial omega, lunate epsilon, use of later Greek ου ligature, use of X for ξ and S for Σ\u003C/p>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line3\">Line 1-3\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"60\" atMost=\"80\">60-80\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line2\">Interlineation line 1 to 2\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"interlinear\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\"/>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                            \u003C/handNote>\n                        \u003C/handDesc>\n                    \u003C/physDesc>\n                    \u003Chistory>\n                        \u003Corigin>\n                            \u003CorigPlace>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"ancient\" ref=\"http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462410\" corresp=\"#findspot\">Panhormus\u003C/placeName>\t\t\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"modern\" ref=\"http://sws.geonames.org/2523920\">Palermo\u003C/placeName>\n                            \t\u003Cgeo>38.13205, 13.33561\u003C/geo>\n\t\t\u003C/origPlace>\n                            \u003CorigDate datingMethod=\"#julian\" notBefore-custom=\"0601\" notAfter-custom=\"0650\" evidence=\"lettering\">Bonacasa dates to first decades of 7th cent CE\u003C/origDate>\n                    